Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid that this day would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.46,0:00:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If an Age of Cosmos were to arrive,\Nwho would stand to benefit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:01:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Lords would lose their Crests,\Nthe Mages would lose their magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the Artists would lose their Art.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else, all of the ordinary people\Nare hoping for an Age of Cosmos!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,During the Age of the Ultimate Chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we fought alongside the humans\Nwith Chaos as our common enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But as Chaos began to fade away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,more and more humans\Nbegan to fight among each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you think will happen\Nif Chaos were to vanish completely?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even in the Age of Cosmos,\Nthere would probably still be wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that would be the decision\Nof the people in that era.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vampire King, didn't you become an Artist\Nso that you could survive the Age of Chaos?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I also intend to go on surviving.\NForever, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Towards that end, I must defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I succeed, the Grancrest will never be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why live at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's only to keep living,\Nthen it's no different than being dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve lost my Art.\NBut my feelings haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll protect my beloved sister,\Nand I'll risk my life to do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Risking my life in order to preserve my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that unacceptable?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying it's unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mother died protecting us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Werewolves always risk their lives\Nto protect their clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll avenge our clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother Aeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The Vampire King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This is his real body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That one over there is just a shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed that you found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I kill this one, that'll extinguish you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give up, Vampire King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't manage to survive\Nbecause I was the most powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because even if I was killed,\NI’ll leave behind shadows, and continue to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge for my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that I'd protect Siluca with my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aishela!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the shadows drain life-force\Nout of anyone they touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- How dare you hurt everyone!\N- We won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If killing your main body doesn't kill you,\Nthen we'll just destroy all of your shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll destroy you this time, Vampire King!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you can, little wolf cubs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:05:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma! Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now all that's left is you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You won’t get your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'll be all right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Priscilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What was that light?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was the Holy Grail's... Priscilla's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now he can't produce any more shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm burning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How dare—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a grudge against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take in all of your Art!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Aeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's end this, Vampire King.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:08:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Aeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Aeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Siluca, please be cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a shadow there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's still one left, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But his Art is starting to fade away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he can't create\Nany new shadows in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma, Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please don't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die! I don't want to, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die! I don't want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's not the one\Nwho killed Mother and Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've already taken our revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head to Eramu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Hubertus?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have a lot of questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About the Great Hall Tragedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How the Order of the Crest\Nand Pandora are connected...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But what I want to know the most
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is why you tried to stop the birth of the Grancrest,\Nand the end of the Age of Chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to know that last answer,\Nyou must touch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It could be a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to find out the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I need to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of what I plan to accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I will accompany you.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But remember,\Nit's what you sense that matters, Sir Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Inside the Chaos Globe, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Are we trapped in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I don't think these are our actual bodies.\NOur minds must be inside the Chaos Glo—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}You must not allow the Age of Chaos to end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is Pandora.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pandora?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must not allow the Age of Chaos to end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This may be the previous civilization, said to have\Nprospered before the Chaos explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.\NA civilization like this from so long ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It is said to have existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But having only seen the records,\Nit seemed more like a fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the Chaos is extinguished,\Nthe technology that we lost can be regained.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the distant future,\Nwe might be able to restore this civilization!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must not allow the Age of Chaos to end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In spite of having contradictions and issues,\Nthis civilization matured as if it had a life of its own.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then one day,\Nthey obtained the ultimate energy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was thought that civilization\Nwould evolve even further.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:14:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that energy came to be used\Nfor weapons, as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The more civilization evolves,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the more its light and darkness\Nbecome stronger, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you insist that the Age of Chaos\Ncan never come to an end?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to stave off the end of the world,\Nwe have made a certain decision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We must flood the world with Chaos,\Nand destroy civilization.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should the Age of Chaos end, humankind\Nwill eventually obtain the ultimate energy again,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the world would certainly be obliterated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must not allow the Age of Chaos to end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That would signal the beginning of the end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must not allow the Age of Chaos to end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must not allow the Age of Chaos to end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must not allow the Age of Chaos to end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably a record of the previous civilization,\Nand a memory of someone named Pandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As well as the Mage Academy's principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should the Age of Chaos come to an end,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the technology of the previous civilization\Nwill eventually be restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate energy will be created,\Nand then utilized as the final weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand now\Nwhy the Age of Chaos was brought on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the Mage Academy's principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't change how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just because the world might end\Nin the distant future,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's not right to sacrifice people living today,\Nand those who haven't even been born yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:16:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it signals the beginning of the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,instead of Chaos, I choose the Age of Cosmos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think that would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Sir Theo, you became a Lord\Nin order to save those suffering under the Chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emperor, is that your decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the beginning of the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please summon the Margrave of Waldlind\Nand the Marquis of Jalucia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to announce the ascension.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As of now, in the name of the great First Lord, Leon,\Nas well as my Crest,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I ascend to the throne of emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this empire is Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I hereby designate Eramu\Nas its imperial capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An emperor is the spokesman of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My goal is to rule so that all of you\Ncan lead safe, just, and happy lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I dreamed for in Sistina,\Nwhere the people suffer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,under the Chaos and oppressive rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This might be just a vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the emperor must adhere to this\Nas his one principle,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and constantly strive to fulfill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the future, if anyone in violation\Nof this principle should become emperor,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I grant the people the right...\NNo, the duty, to overthrow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the people must follow the empire's principles,\Njust as the emperor does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of the emperor,\NI ask all Lords to pledge allegiance to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And after all Crests have been unified,\Nand the true Grancrest has been created,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I swear to bring an end to the Age of Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,THREE YEARS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I now pronounce you husband and wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You may now kiss the bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here and now,\Ntwo couples have been joined in matrimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The emperor has fulfilled his promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He has transformed\Nthe Great Hall Tragedy into a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The continent has been unified, and all Crests\Nare now in the hands of the emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Today, at this moment, the Emperor's Holy Seal,\Nthe Grancrest, will be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so the Chaos that had overrun\Nthe continent was purged,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}and at last,\Npeace came to the world momentarily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The First Emperor abdicated in favor\Nof the Second Emperor, Alexis Doucet,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}while Marrine, his wife,\Nwas appointed chancellor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Eramu's rule was entrusted to them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After abdicating, Theo Cornaro\Nreturned to rule over Sistina, his homeland.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to bring happiness to his homeland,\Nhe had changed the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd dreamed of seeing this for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.37,0:22:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.08,0:22:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've carried through magnificently, Sir Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:23:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca, my witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was you who cast the best spell of all\Non this former wandering Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From hereon, time will flow peacefully,\Nin a calm pace, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.15,0:23:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GRANCREST
